  "text": "The van't Hoff plots for the hydration reactions of protonated 2SU, 4SU, and 6Me2SU are shown in Fig. 2 , and the thermochemical data obtained from these van't Hoff plots are summarized in Table 1 [CITATION_1] . d Calculated values at the MP2(full)/6-311+G(2d,2p) level of theory using MP2(full)/6-31G* optimized geometries, Reference [CITATION_2] . e Exp. from Reference [CITATION_3] . f Exp. from Reference [CITATION_4] . g Exp. from Reference [CITATION_5] . h Reference [CITATION_6] . I Reference [CITATION_7] . j Reference [CITATION_8] . This suggests that the O4H position could be the favorable site for a water molecule binding, 1b, as schematically depicted in Scheme 2.",
